These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, writing, photography, card-games
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, ice-hockey, snowboarding, skateboarding
1. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not to the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##8
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not the person who's hobby is photography##6
5. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##5
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | card-games  | woodworking | photography | writing  |
| Sport   | climbing | snowboarding   | skateboarding  | ice-hockey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
There 4 different types of food: spinach, banana, pomegranate, grapefruit
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, fisherman, electrician, engineer
1. the engineer is not to the left of the engineer##8
2. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapefruit##5
3. the person eating spinach is the fisherman##1
4. the person eating grapefruit is between the person eating spinach and the person eating banana##2
5. the person eating banana is somewhere between the person eating pomegranate and the librarian##7
6. the electrician is somewhere to the left of the person eating banana##5
7. the librarian is not to the left of the librarian##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Food   | pomegranate | banana          | grapefruit | spinach     |
| Job    | electrician      | engineer | librarian | fisherman |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, accountant, coach, chef
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, zombie, epic, scientific
1. the person watching animation movies is not to the left of the coach##8
2. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left##1
3. the accountant is on the right of the designer##1
4. the accountant is in an even position##4
5. the chef is on the far left or far right##3
6. the designer is somewhere to the left of the person watching scientific movies##5
7. the chef is the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Job           | designer | accountant | coach     | chef |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie    | scientific   | animation | epic    |

