.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, pop, soul, jazz
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, skiing, volleyball, basketball
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is not to the left of the person who's sport is skiing##8
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the fan of pop##1
4. the fan of jazz is not to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##8
5. the fan of country is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
6. the fan of country is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
7. the fan of soul is somewhere to the left of the fan of jazz##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | soul   | pop         | jazz   | country    |
| Sport         | skiing | basketball | volleyball | biathlon |

