.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, western, mystery, fantasy
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, parkour, skiing, weightlifting
1. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere between the person watching crime movies and the person watching western movies##7
2. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is skiing##5
3. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere between the person watching mystery movies and the person watching crime movies##7
4. the person watching mystery movies is not to the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##8
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere between the person watching western movies and the person who's sport is parkour##7
6. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the right of the person watching fantasy movies##5
7. the person who's sport is parkour is not to the left of the person watching crime movies##8
8. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person watching fantasy movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | western   | mystery | fantasy | crime    |
| Sport         | rowing | weightlifting   | skiing   | parkour |

