3. the chef is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
4. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere between the person who's sport is handball and the chef##7
5. the paramedic is not to the right of the freelancer##8
6. the freelancer is somewhere between the person who's sport is handball and the paramedic##7

.:: Answer ::.
