.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, ambient, metal, jazz
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, ship, jet-ski, subway
1. the fan of r&b is between the fan of jazz and the person driving the scooter##2
2. the person driving the subway is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
4. the fan of ambient is somewhere to the right of the person driving the scooter##5
5. the person driving the ship is the person driving the ship##1
6. the fan of metal is not the person driving the jet-ski##6
7. the fan of jazz is not to the right of the fan of metal##8
8. the person driving the scooter is not to the left of the person driving the ship##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | jazz   | r&b | metal | ambient |
| Transport     | subway | ship       | scooter  | jet-ski    |

