.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, orange, avocado, plum
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, gardening, drawing, singing
1. the person eating avocado is not to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##8
2. the person who's hobby is chess is not to the right of the person eating orange##8
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the right of the person eating plum##5
4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating avocado is between the person who's hobby is singing and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
6. the person eating orange is on the far left##1
7. the person eating avocado is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | orange        | plum | avocado      | cranberry    |
| Hobby   | chess | drawing   | gardening | singing |

