.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, coffee, milk, mirinda
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, baseball, tennis, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not to the right of the person who's sport is golf##8
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not to the right of the person drinking lemonade##8
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere between the person who's sport is tennis and the person drinking coffee##7
7. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
8. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | mirinda | coffee         | milk    | lemonade       |
| Sport      | baseball | weightlifting | golf | tennis |

