.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, peas, banana, asparagus
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, animation, thriller, time-travel
 1. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching thriller movies##5
 2. the person eating asparagus is not to the left of the person eating banana##8
 3. the person eating avocado is the person watching thriller movies##1
 4. the person watching thriller movies is not to the right of the person watching animation movies##8
 5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person eating peas##1
 6. the person watching animation movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating banana##5
 7. the person watching animation movies is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating avocado is not to the right of the person watching thriller movies##8
 9. the person watching animation movies is not to the left of the person eating avocado##8
10. the person eating peas is not to the left of the person watching scientific movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Food          | peas    | banana | avocado | asparagus |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | time-travel  | thriller     | animation    |

