2. the person eating pomegranate is not to the left of the person who's hobby is photography##8
3. the person who's hobby is photography is the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the person who's hobby is writing is the person eating banana##1
5. the person eating banana is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
