.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-19::.
4 different pets are kept: pony, frog, rat, mouse
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, airplane, bus, skateboard
1. the owner of the mouse is not the person driving the bus##6
2. the person driving the bus is not to the right of the owner of the rat##8
3. the owner of the frog is somewhere between the owner of the rat and the owner of the mouse##7
4. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the right of the owner of the pony##5
5. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the left of the person driving the skateboard##5
6. the person driving the van is not to the right of the person driving the airplane##8
7. the owner of the frog is not to the left of the person driving the skateboard##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Pet         | pony  | mouse | frog  | rat  |
| Transport   | van | airplane   | skateboard | bus |

