.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different pets are kept: lizard, goldfish, horse, mouse
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, taxi, snowmobile, boat
1. the person driving the taxi is not the owner of the lizard##6
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
3. the owner of the mouse is not to the left of the person driving the boat##8
4. the owner of the horse is the person driving the ship##1
5. the owner of the mouse is somewhere between the person driving the taxi and the person driving the ship##7
6. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
7. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person driving the boat and the owner of the horse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | goldfish    | mouse | lizard | horse |
| Transport   | taxi | boat      | snowmobile     | ship     |

 